Package com.newsalligator.model

Class ArticleData

java.lang.Object
com.newsalligator.model.ArticleData
public class ArticleData extends Object

ArticleData

The ArticleData class is a class for storing and preprocessing data related to an article.
Author:
Phong Au, Quan Tran

  • Constructor Details

    • ArticleData

      public ArticleData(String link, String websiteSource, String image, String type, String summary, String title, String intro, String detailedContent, String tags, String authorName, String category, String creationDate, String htmlContentLocation)
      Creates an ArticleData object with desired details from an article.
      Parameters:
      link - the link of the article
      websiteSource - the source web of the article
      image - the thumbnail of the article
      type - the type of the article (blogs, article news, tweets,...)
      summary - the summary of the article
      title - the title of the article
      intro - the introduction of the article
      detailedContent - the detail content of the article
      tags - the tags of the article
      authorName - the name of the author of the article
      category - the category of the article
      creationDate - the create date of the article
      htmlContentLocation - the fetched HTML content location of the web
